             <h1 class="text-left">Critiques and Comments:</h1> 
             <h3 class="h3-section-info text-left">
             Critiques and comments can be posted on every photograph and is encouraged. By commenting on and critiquing work, we can inspire and encourage each other to keep shooting and improve our craft. Share the love, people.
             </h3>
