             <h1 class="text-left">Photo-centric, rather than Profile-centric:</h1> 
             <h3 class="h3-section-info text-left">
             We’ve all seen famous celebs post mundane images of a piece of a cake and get like a zillion likes, this isn’t how it works here. Chimper is a level playing field, there are no categories, no hierarchy, no following or fans. It’s all about the photographs. So why not be a part of it? Put it out there. Show the world. It’s time to be a little bit epic.
             </h3>
